      <h1><i>ENVIRONMENTAL SUSTAINABILITY</i></h1>
      <section id="What_Is">
        <h3 class="karma-medium" style="text-align: center;"><i>Environmental sustainability refers to the responsible management of natural resources to fulfill current needs without compromising the ability of future generations to meet their needs.</i></h3>
      </section>
